PSXTextLiteral.text: MMM dd, yyyy hh:mm a zzzz

PSXDataSelector.nativeStatement: select CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.CONTENTSTATUSHISTORYID, CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.CONTENTID, CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.SESSIONID, CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.ACTOR, CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.VALID, CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.STATEID, CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.TRANSITIONID, CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.ROLENAME, CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.CHECKOUTUSERNAME, CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.LASTMODIFIERNAME, CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.LASTMODIFIEDDATE, CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.EVENTTIME, CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.WORKFLOWAPPID, CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.TITLE, STATES.STATENAME, TRANSITIONS.TRANSITIONDESC from CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY, STATES, TRANSITIONS where CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.STATEID *= STATES.STATEID and CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.WORKFLOWAPPID *= STATES.WORKFLOWAPPID and CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.TRANSITIONID *= TRANSITIONS.TRANSITIONID and CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.WORKFLOWAPPID *= TRANSITIONS.WORKFLOWAPPID and CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY.CONTENTID=:"PSXParam/contentid" order by CONTENTSTATUSHISTORYID
SELECT CONTENTID, MAX(REVISIONID) AS REVISIONID FROM CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY WHERE CONTENTID IN (:"PSXSingleParam/sys_contentid") AND (VALID = 'Y' OR VALID = 'y') GROUP BY CONTENTID

PSXDataSet.name: putLastPublicRev
PSXDataSet.description: Update the PUBLIC_REVISION column in CONTENTSTATUS table
